data.chText: 用之不竭的；无穷无尽的
data.enText: that cannot be exhausted (= finished); very great
an inexhaustible supply of good jokes

tr: incapable of being entirely consumed or used up
that cannot be entirely consumed or used up

value.def: If there is an inexhaustible supply of something, there is so much of it that it cannot all be used up.

example.ex: She has an inexhaustible supply of enthusiasm...
His energy was unbounded and his patience inexhaustible.
example.tran: 他有无穷的精力和无限的耐心。
